CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771981383
OL,3,CMSPs to back Holyrood Budget that
OL,4,CShona Robison says will 'make lives
OL,5,Cbetter'
OL,7,FMs Robison however said the Scottish
OL,8,FGovernment's package of measures "is
OL,9,Ffocused on delivering for the people
OL,10,Fof Scotland ` driving improvements in
OL,11,Four NHS and providing real support
OL,12,Fwith the cost of living".
OL,14,FSpeaking about the Budget plans, she
OL,15,Fsaid these would "continue to improve
OL,16,Faccess to healthcare with funding for
OL,17,Fa network of 16 walk-in GP clinics
OL,18,Fopen seven days a week, and expands
OL,19,Four landmark efforts to eradicate
OL,20,Fchild poverty by increasing the
OL,21,FScottish child payment".
OL,26,@pD@bOUtD@XO]wD@ROU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771981383
OL,3,CMSPs to back Holyrood Budget that
OL,4,CShona Robison says will 'make lives
OL,5,Cbetter'
OL,7,FThe Finance Secretary added: "The
OL,8,FBudget will make lives better for
OL,9,Fpeople in Scotland and our plans mean
OL,10,Fthat 55% of taxpayers can expect to
OL,11,Fpay less income tax than in the rest
OL,12,Fof the UK."
OL,14,FMs Robison, speaking ahead of
OL,15,FWednesday's vote, said: "It is a
OL,16,FBudget worthy of support and I urge
OL,17,FParliament to back it today."
OL,26,@oD@^OUtD@KO]wD@YOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
