PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771981383
OL,3,CMSPs to back Holyrood Budget that
OL,4,CShona Robison says will 'make lives
OL,5,Cbetter'
OL,7,FScottish Liberal Democrat economy
OL,8,Fspokesperson Jamie Greene said he
OL,9,Fwould back it after "securing #300
OL,10,Fmillion in funding for a range of Lib
OL,11,FDem priorities including business
OL,12,Frates relief, social care, young
OL,13,Fentrepreneurs, hospices and our vital
OL,14,Fcolleges".
OL,26,@qD@UOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
