OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771981383
OL,3,CMSPs to back Holyrood Budget that
OL,4,CShona Robison says will 'make lives
OL,5,Cbetter'
OL,7,FMr Greene said: "When it became clear
OL,8,Fthat this Budget would pass anyway
OL,9,Fbecause Labour walked away from the
OL,10,Fnegotiating table, the Scottish
OL,11,FLiberal Democrats promised that we
OL,12,Fwould squeeze it for every penny to
OL,13,Fdeliver for people across the country
OL,14,F` and that is exactly what we have
OL,15,Fdone.
OL,17,F"Neither the Scottish Conservatives
OL,18,Fnor Scottish Labour got a penny
OL,19,Fbecause neither cared about using
OL,20,Ftheir leverage in opposition to fight
OL,21,Ffor more money for their priorities."
OL,26,@oD@QOUyD@AOU}D@eO]
